data.title: SUPERMARIONATION: THE GERRY & SYLVIA ANDERSON COLLECTION
data.meta_description: Gerry and Sylvia Anderson, creators of the legendary supermarionation series The Thunderbirds, lent their prolific genius to a host of spy and sci-fi puppetry shows in the 1960s that brilliantly played out heroic adventure stories within futuristic, fantastical universes. data.text: Madman acknowledges the Traditional Owners, the Wurundjeri and Boon Wurrung people of the Kulin Nation, on whose land we meet, share and work. We pay our respects to Elders past and present and extend our respect to Aboriginal and Torres Strait Islander people from all nations of this land. Aboriginal and Torres Strait Islander peoples should be aware that this website may contain images or names of people who have since passed away.
